name: cute vae
description:
I started merging vae because I wanted a color that was somewhere between counterfeit and barrymix, and eventually found what I was looking for!

Add --no-half-vae if it fails to work

+In response to feedback I've created a comparison table with other VAEs! If you'd like a slightly larger table, I'll make it a bit larger! (i did not use Dynamic Thresholding to compare all results.) These results are from using the unweighted imputation verybadimagenegative_v1.3. If a different embedding is used, you may see different results

visit me on Twitter -> https://twitter.com/nzxt_cam
